<style>
  td { vertical-align: middle; }

  .token-name { white-space: nowrap; }

  /* Color swatches */
  .color-name {
    font-weight: var(--wa-font-weight-semibold);
    margin-block-end: var(--wa-space-2xs);
  }
  ul.color-group {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .color-group {
    align-items: start;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: nowrap;
    gap: var(--wa-space-3xs);
  }
  .color-group small {
    font-size: var(--wa-font-size-xs);
    color: var(--wa-color-text-quiet);
  }
  .color-preview {
    flex: 1 1 auto;
  }

  /* Spacing preview */
  .spacing-example {
    --dot-size: 0.5em;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    background-color: var(--wa-color-neutral-fill-normal);
    height: 2em;
    margin-inline: var(--dot-size);
  }
  .spacing-example::before {
    content: '';
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    width: var(--dot-size);
    background-color: var(--wa-color-neutral-fill-loud);
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-inline-start: calc(var(--dot-size) * -1);
  }
  .spacing-example::after {
    content: '';
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    width: var(--dot-size);
    background-color: var(--wa-color-neutral-fill-loud);
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-inline-end: calc(var(--dot-size) * -1);
  }

  /* Transition preview */
  .transition-swatch {
    background-color: var(--wa-color-neutral-fill-normal);
    border: none;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .transition-swatch::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    background-color: var(--wa-color-brand-fill-loud);
    border-radius: var(--wa-border-radius-m);
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 0;
    height: 100%;
    transition: inherit;
  }
  .transition-swatch:hover::after {
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* Color mix preview */
  .color-mix-example {
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(
        to right,
        color-mix(in oklab, transparent, var(--mix-color)) 25%,
        color-mix(in oklab, var(--wa-color-brand-fill-loud), var(--mix-color)) 25%,
        color-mix(in oklab, var(--wa-color-brand-fill-loud), var(--mix-color)) 75%,
        var(--wa-color-brand-fill-loud) 75%
      );
    border: none;
    color: var(--wa-color-brand-on-loud);
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Key color row */
  .key-color-group .color-preview small {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--wa-font-size-xs);
    color: var(--wa-color-text-quiet);
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }

  /* On-color swatches */
  .on-color-group {
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--wa-space-xs);
  }
  .on-color-preview {
    flex: 1 1 8rem;
    min-width: 7rem;
  }
  .on-color-swatch {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: var(--wa-space-s) var(--wa-space-s);
    border-radius: var(--wa-border-radius-m);
    font-weight: var(--wa-font-weight-semibold);
    font-size: var(--wa-font-size-m);
  }
  .on-color-preview small {
    display: block;
    margin-block-start: var(--wa-space-3xs);
    font-size: var(--wa-font-size-xs);
    color: var(--wa-color-text-quiet);
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }

  /* Token tables */
  .token-table { width: 100%; }
  .token-table th, .token-table td { padding: var(--wa-space-xs) var(--wa-space-s); }
  .token-table th { text-align: start; font-weight: var(--wa-font-weight-semibold); }

  /* Tab panel spacing */
  p { max-width: var(--content-width-s); }
  wa-tab-panel > * + * {
    margin-block-start: var(--wa-content-spacing);
  }

  /* ── Search bar ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .token-search-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--wa-space-s);
    margin-block: var(--wa-space-l);
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(var(--header-height) + var(--subheader-height));
    padding-block: var(--wa-space-xs);
    background-color: var(--wa-color-surface-default);
    z-index: 10;
  }
  .token-search-bar wa-input { flex: 1; }
  .token-search-count { font-size: var(--wa-font-size-s); color: var(--wa-color-text-quiet); white-space: nowrap; }

  /* ── Search results ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .result-row { cursor: pointer; }
  .result-row:hover td { background: var(--wa-color-surface-lowered); }

  /* ── Category badges ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .cat-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.15em 0.55em;
    border-radius: var(--wa-border-radius-pill);
    font-size: var(--wa-font-size-xs);
    font-weight: var(--wa-font-weight-semibold);
    white-space: nowrap;
    background: var(--wa-color-neutral-fill-normal);
    color: var(--wa-color-neutral-on-normal);
  }
  .cat-badge-color      { background: var(--wa-color-brand-fill-quiet);    color: var(--wa-color-brand-on-quiet); }
  .cat-badge-typography { background: var(--wa-color-success-fill-quiet);   color: var(--wa-color-success-on-quiet); }
  .cat-badge-space      { background: var(--wa-color-warning-fill-quiet);   color: var(--wa-color-warning-on-quiet); }
  .cat-badge-borders    { background: var(--wa-color-danger-fill-quiet);    color: var(--wa-color-danger-on-quiet); }
  .cat-badge-shadows    { background: var(--wa-color-neutral-fill-normal);  color: var(--wa-color-neutral-on-normal); }
  .cat-badge-focus      { background: var(--wa-color-brand-fill-normal);    color: var(--wa-color-brand-on-normal); }
  .cat-badge-transitions{ background: var(--wa-color-success-fill-normal);  color: var(--wa-color-success-on-normal); }
  .cat-badge-components { background: var(--wa-color-warning-fill-normal);  color: var(--wa-color-warning-on-normal); }

  /* ── Row highlight after search-navigate ─────────────────────── */
  @keyframes token-highlight {
    0%   { background-color: var(--wa-color-brand-fill-quiet); }
    100% { background-color: transparent; }
  }
  .token-row-highlight { animation: token-highlight 1.8s ease-out forwards; }
</style>

{% markdown %}
Design tokens are CSS custom properties that thread through Web Awesome's components to give your theme a consistent look and feel. By overriding these properties, you can customize the entire component library without touching individual component styles.

To customize a token, set its value in your stylesheet:

```css
:root {
  --wa-font-family-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  --wa-border-width-scale: 1.5;
  --wa-space-scale: 1.25;
}
```
{% endmarkdown %}

